// TOTP (Time-based One-Time Password) API for the Hades schema registry.
//
// TOTP enrollment is a two-step process:
//  1. BeginEnrollTOTP  - server generates and returns the TOTP secret and
//     backup codes. The secret is stored encrypted (AES-256-GCM) but the
//     enrollment is not yet active.
//  2. ConfirmEnrollTOTP - caller proves possession by submitting the first
//     valid code from their authenticator app. Only then is TOTP enabled.
//
// Once enabled, login returns pending_totp=true and the caller must call
// VerifyTOTP to obtain a fully authenticated session token.

